    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee uſwelk fatwu Mehli ka Stohpu us Melleem/ un ne us Pateefibu/ tee tohp warreni wirs Semmes/ jo tee dohdahs no weena Launuuna uhs ohtru/ bet mannis tee ne paſthst/ fatka tas KUNGS.\n"
